.TH INFINIFIX 1 "March 2026" "InfiniFix v0.2 beta" "User Commands"
.SH NAME
infinifix \- Huawei Linux Doctor
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B infinifix
[\-\-dry\-run] [\-\-version]
.I command
[options]
.SH DESCRIPTION
InfiniFix is a terminal-first diagnostics and repair tool for Huawei and Honor laptops on Linux.
.br
Project: https://github.com/lnfiniware/Infinifix
.SH COMMANDS
.TP
.B doctor
Interactive guided diagnostics and safe fix preview.
.TP
.B report
Generate a diagnostic tarball.
.TP
.B apply
Apply safe fixes.
.TP
.B apply \-\-all
Apply safe and advanced fixes after warnings.
.TP
.B revert
Restore latest backup session.
.TP
.B status
Show last run state and changed items.
.SH FILES
.TP
.B /var/lib/infinifix/backups/
Timestamped backup sessions.
.TP
.B /var/log/infinifix/reports/
Diagnostic report tarballs.
.SH EXIT STATUS
0 on success, non-zero on failure.
